Interface SiteSetupQuestion

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SiteSetupQuestionImpl

    public interface SiteSetupQuestion
extends Serializable
    The SiteSetupQuestion object is to store user-defined question. A question would have two parts: the question part and the list of answers
    Author:
    zqian
